<seg id="149">The second highest number was within 90 days from the date of lodging the asylum application (17.61%).</seg>
<seg id="150">In total, 73% of asylum procedures initiated in 2001-2003 were finally decided within one year from their start.</seg>
<seg id="151">Within two years from the start of the asylum procedure, 92% of asylum applications were finally decided.</seg>
