<seg id="112">4. Value added tax administration in the Czech Republic and Germany</seg>
<seg id="113">Registration of payers in the Czech Republic</seg>
<seg id="114">A) Taxpayers having their registered office, place of business or establishment in the Czech Republic</seg>
<seg id="115">According to Act No. 337/1992 Coll., on the Administration of Taxes and Fees (hereinafter “Act No. 337/1992 Coll.”), a taxpayer, taxpayer and legal successor of a natural or legal person, which is defined as a tax entity by law.</seg>
<seg id="116">As of 31 December 2004, a total of 421,865 tax subjects were registered for VAT in the Czech Republic.</seg>
