<seg id="118">A taxable person having his registered office, place of business or establishment in the Czech Republic, whose turnover exceeds CZK 1,000,000 (EUR 33,575) for the next 12 preceding consecutive calendar months, becomes a taxpayer from the 1st day of the third month following the month in which he exceeded the registration limit (Section 94, subsection 1 of Act No. 235/2004 Coll., on Value Added Tax; hereinafter “Act No. 235/2004 Coll.”).</seg>
