<seg id="123">Conditions for registration of tax payers should be harmonised within the EU</seg>
<seg id="124">Based on the results of the previous audit, the SAO recommended modification of the conditions for registration for VAT and introduction of a new rule for cancellation of registration in the Czech Republic.</seg>
