<seg id="144">Sharing of successful criteria, components and approaches of the risk management system at EU level</seg>
<seg id="145">Proper collection of VAT is one of the prerequisites for the proper functioning of the EU internal market.</seg>
<seg id="146">The fight against VAT fraud is therefore one of the priority areas of interest and has received considerable attention in recent years.</seg>
<seg id="147">The importance of this fight is evidenced by the conclusions of a study published by the European Commission in October 2009, in which an external evaluator attempted to determine the difference between the eligible and actually collected VAT levels in the 25 EU Member States (hereinafter referred to as the EU-25) during the period 2000-2006.</seg>
